headline.main: Rocket Man Is Honored By Russians; Saw Into Our Future' Planned a Jet Engine

results.snippet: When the Soyuz team of Soviet cosmonauts returns to earth from its rendezvous next July with the Apollo crew of American astronauts, one of the first formal stops will almost certainly be thispleasant city.
